<div><h2><u>Description:</u></h2>
<h3>
Abstract Art refers to a Style of Painting that does not use figurative reality as a reference.Instead,the Artist alludes to their subject & reduces it to a simplified form.Colors and shapes are used to portray emotions and the landscape of one's inner world.Abstract Paintings are emotionally intense and spontaneously created by the artist.they are often synonymous with action or gesture paintings that have an high drama in their composition.the colors are the subjects themselves and they are normally painted on large canvas material.</h3>
